          <p id="WFTU.IO.25">The Federation was founded in 1945. It aims to defend the rights of workers and retired workers worldwide, to strengthen solidarity among the trade union movement, to promote socioeconomic development, and to combat all forms of subservience, exploitation and oppression.</p>
          <int-org-section id="WFTU.IO.42" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
